            <div class="container">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p class="font14 align">
                        The growth status of children is a measure of the health and well being of the whole community. Having recognised the need of identifying and controlling child malnutrition.
                        <br />
                        <br />
                        RAMINFO has now come up with “EPGM” an innovation that brings Huge Change in Growth Monitoring Data Collection from Anganwadi Centers as the successful cycle of malnutrition control starts with flawless data collection.EPGM is the meaningful, accurate and non intrusive way to perform Growth Monitoring of babies, Children and adults at Last  Mile Monitoring Centre (LMMC) automatically.


                    </p>
                    <p class="font14 align">
                        This eases the Growth Monitoring work of Anganwadi worker there by making her concentrate on improving the nutritional status of Mother and Child rather than spending her time in maintaining registers and preparation of consolidated reports.
                        <br />
                        <br />
                        Government also get real time reports on Nutritional Status of beneficiaries across the State.                    
                    </p>


                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="margin-top">
                        <img src="/Content/images/slide2.png" class="img-responsive" style="margin-top: 20%;" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

